{"tid":2318204,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支那武肺疫苗在阿聯酋獲批註冊上市 抗感染率86% 轉抗體率99%","createTime":"2020-12-09T07:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T08:09:54.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ac6986f7d9a92e1353e88a60c5cb057dcf4c7e88","tid":2318204,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T07:10:15.000Z","msg":"中國生物新冠疫苗在阿聯酋獲批註冊上市<br />\n<br />\n中國生物研發的新型冠狀毒疫苗，在阿聯酋獲批註冊上市。報道指，阿聯酋當局已覆核中國生物提交的第3期臨床試驗數據，資料涵蓋125個國籍、約3.1萬名志願者，顯示疫苗對抗病毒感染有效性為8成6，中和抗體轉陽率為9成9，能夠百份百預防出現中度和重度病徵，研究亦沒發現疫苗存在嚴重安全隱患。<br />\n<br />\n中國生物疫苗今年9月，已經在阿聯酋獲得緊急使用授權，以保護前線醫護。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2369938\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2369938&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUHKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=74362ff0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2369938</a>"},{"pid":"89b7d5a8d66894c309b40588c8b6e34cf03008a1","tid":2318204,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T07:10:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1dd47603df8157e327663f646ea53d430fe21f","tid":2318204,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:06:36.000Z","msg":"感覺現今世代變左不要問只要信<br />\n<br />\n以前講科學都解釋下抗體係對病毒點發揮作用<br />\n<br />\n如果病毒常常變種，其實對變種病毒會唔會失去功能，變成同流感疫苗一樣"},{"pid":"e64eca24ff98c349c369f61326018f06c74a2f39","tid":2318204,"uid":154756,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:09:54.000Z","msg":"中和抗體轉陽率為9成9？<br />\n唔明"}]}